{"tid":2346351,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梅艷芳離世17周年丨袁詠儀連續十年發文悼念 何韻詩發噩夢抽籤送死","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:14:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"764eecae803414c12b8d13e25f4abdd4f185c626","tid":2346351,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"袁詠儀（靚靚）曾經梅姐合作拍電影《金枝玉葉2》而成為好友，每年梅姐的生忌和死忌，她都在網上留言，她凌晨時份在社交平台留言：「梅姐，你好嗎？ 」有網民留言讚靚靚很有心，發現她已連續10年出post懷念故友。<br />\n<br />\n徒弟蔡一傑亦上載與梅姐同台演出的片段並說：「阿梅，又到了妳的忌辰，美好回憶仍然在腦海中盤旋，miss you，妳在天之靈保佑我哋全香港大眾市民個個身體健康，疫情快過去！」蔡一智和蘇志威有留言。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/6IHSJSL2LJBTLPYAAMQJRES2DU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2F6IHSJSL2LJBTLPYAAMQJRES2DU%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=2a5e332b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2F6IHSJSL2LJBTLPYAAMQJRES2DU%2F&h=4e218de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/6IHSJSL2LJBTLPYAAMQJRES2DU/</a>"},{"pid":"567a124239706accf27b2028cd4c74ce19819d1d","tid":2346351,"uid":25560,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"可以停止消費死者嗎?"},{"pid":"078bd22648d577417ff1a2ad67258fd1d0e36fb1","tid":2346351,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"情懷未變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a547f38b742517ba836f2273c55165333268dd","tid":2346351,"uid":151926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"個腦loop緊相愛很難"},{"pid":"2b4ec4924fa81ea2e85ada4b4b9b41bbe90bed90","tid":2346351,"uid":36583,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"567a124239706accf27b2028cd4c74ce19819d1d","tid":2346351,"uid":25560,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":